quotes.title: Nature of reality
quotes.quote: The whole creation is made up of trio. The three elements of the nature unite as trio create this Triatic creation.
quotes.author: Acharya Mahanidhi

quotes.title: testing
quotes.quote: हास्यशीलतावृद्धये च इयं रचना किञ्चित्करी चेत् अयं लेखकः कृतार्थः नूनम् ।
quotes.author: Gurunatha ji

quotes.title: Bannanje Acharya on Trivrut
quotes.quote: The world is made up of Trivrut.
